menuItems.name: Mushroom Bruschetta
menuItems.description: Indulge in the earthy flavors of our Mushroom Bruschetta. Sautéed mushrooms seasoned with garlic and thyme are piled onto crispy baguette slices, creating a savory bite-sized delight.

menuItems.name: Sweet Potato Bites
menuItems.description: Experience a blend of sweet and savory with our Sweet Potato Bites. Roasted sweet potato rounds are topped with goat cheese and a drizzle of honey, creating a mouthwatering combination of flavors.

menuItems.name: Brussels Sprouts Sliders
menuItems.description: Elevate your vegetable game with our Brussels Sprouts Sliders. Crispy roasted Brussels sprouts are sandwiched between slider buns with a tangy aioli, creating a unique and delicious appetizer.

menuItems.name: Truffle Parmesan Popcorn
menuItems.description: Upgrade your popcorn game with our Truffle Parmesan Popcorn. Freshly popped corn is drizzled with truffle oil and sprinkled with grated Parmesan, creating a gourmet snack that's perfect for any gathering.

menuItems.name: Caprese Skewers
menuItems.description: Savor the flavors of Italy with our Caprese Skewers. Fresh mozzarella, cherry tomatoes, and basil leaves are threaded onto skewers and drizzled with balsamic glaze for a delightful and refreshing appetizer.

menuItems.name: Spinach Artichoke Cups
menuItems.description: Enjoy the classic combination of spinach and artichoke in our Spinach Artichoke Cups. These bite-sized cups feature a creamy filling nestled in a crispy phyllo shell, making them a perfect party appetizer.

menuItems.name: Avocado Shrimp Ceviche
menuItems.description: Transport your taste buds to the coast with our Avocado Shrimp Ceviche. Fresh shrimp, avocado, and citrusy flavors come together in this refreshing and zesty appetizer that's perfect for seafood lovers.

menuItems.name: Stuffed Jalapeños
menuItems.description: Add a spicy kick to your gathering with our Stuffed Jalapeños. Fresh jalapeños are filled with a creamy cheese and bacon mixture, then baked to perfection for a delicious and satisfying appetizer.

menuItems.name: Crispy Zucchini Fritters
menuItems.description: Experience the crunch of our Crispy Zucchini Fritters. Grated zucchini is mixed with herbs and breadcrumbs, fried until golden brown. Served with a tangy dipping sauce, these fritters are a crowd-pleaser.

menuItems.name: Teriyaki Glazed Meatballs
menuItems.description: Delight in the sweet and savory blend of our Teriyaki Glazed Meatballs. Succulent meatballs are coated in a luscious teriyaki glaze, creating a mouthwatering appetizer that's perfect for any occasion.

menuItems.name: Cucumber Feta Rolls
menuItems.description: Refresh your palate with our Cucumber Feta Rolls. Thin cucumber slices are rolled with a creamy feta and dill filling, creating a light and refreshing appetizer that's perfect for warm weather occasions.

menuItems.name: Pesto Stuffed Mushrooms
menuItems.description: Delight in the rich flavors of our Pesto Stuffed Mushrooms. Button mushrooms are filled with a savory mixture of pesto, cream cheese, and breadcrumbs, creating a crowd-pleasing appetizer.
